{"tid":863978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[雙重標準]中國曾擔心玫瑰園計劃造價太高","createTime":"2018-10-16T02:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T02:26:34.000Z","uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c863c72016eb32c7d629a71ed636e3d8257ffc3","tid":863978,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"source wiki<br />\n<br />\n香港機場核心計劃又簡稱「新機場計劃」，於1989年由香港政府宣佈，由於此份計劃描繪將來像玫瑰園般美好，故此又稱為「玫瑰園計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n計劃原預算逾2,000億港元，當計劃公佈時，香港社會譁然，中華人民共和國政府擔心新機場的造價過高，將會影響將來的香港特別行政區政府的財政儲備而對此表示強烈不滿。"},{"pid":"7f227911780b646a0114df00aaba0cb916f10f33","tid":863978,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"預算都只係2000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b72788d938234e69f3c3a463a3df50e05d9ae8c","tid":863978,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829263ad3fbbddb03d35b0e0b6fe2e46e325d480","tid":863978,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f227911780b646a0114df00aaba0cb916f10f33","tid":863978,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"預算都只係2000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"當年2000億好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0aa317b1ccde8b01dce7b9ea94dd40cd8a4dba","tid":863978,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f227911780b646a0114df00aaba0cb916f10f33","tid":863978,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"預算都只係2000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"又唔係<br />\n